# Implementation Guardrails
- Reuse existing code paths; avoid duplication.
- Keep files focused and small; SRP first.
- Contract-first: update shared contract/types before API/client changes.
- Validate external inputs at the boundary; map to domain errors once.
- UI: keep styling consistent with existing tokens and layout patterns.
- Tests: add or update tests for behavior changes.
